{"tid":114002,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"孔劉交過3任女朋友 直言看見「手腳指都漂亮的女生」會心動!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-09T12:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T01:57:40.000Z","uid":9573,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"939ef24cc70061bfb33d0323989e6772077f3445","tid":114002,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62406/58995195020a7.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62406%2F58995195020a7.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=1b81f5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年以電影《屍速列車》走紅全亞洲的 37 歲韓國男演員孔劉，絕對可以說是當今韓國最受到觀眾喜愛的大叔之一，他在去年底主演的電視劇《孤單又燦爛的神－鬼怪》中深情的角色，又再度帶來高人氣的討論度，身為「黃金單身漢」的他，戀愛方面的八卦理所當然也相當受到粉絲矚目，最近就在訪問中被問到他喜歡的理想類型。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62406/5899519c4fcdd.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62406%2F5899519c4fcdd.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=cf36e084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼孔劉身高 184 公分，身材高大挺拔之外，脫下衣服後更擁有健美的肌肉身材，過去他就曾秀出冰塊格般的腹肌，同時帶有反差感的孔劉又擁有陽光般的暖男笑容，雖然未必是公認的超級帥哥，卻意外讓大量女性粉絲迷戀到無法自拔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62406/5899519a0c477.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62406%2F5899519a0c477.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=e9f4c5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔劉在訪問中透露雖然自己已經 37 歲，其實在感情生活中只交過 3 任女朋友，都是個性溫順、小鳥依人的女孩類型，同時很慢熱的屯門瓏門車位188萬元成交他也不太會發生一見鍾情的情況，這反而讓他看待每一段戀情都非常慎重的性格，或許也是他交往對象偏少而持久的原因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62406/58995181dd416.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62406%2F58995181dd416.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=4737d193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那孔劉看到什麼樣的女孩特徵會特別心動呢？孔劉笑著表示自己是「外貌協會」，喜歡聰明又漂亮的女生，同時會讓他心動不已的小癖好就是「對於手指和腳指都漂亮的女生無法抵抗」。孔劉談到的這些條件讓不少網友笑說：「我的唯一優點只有手腳指漂亮，這樣可以嗎？」、「我已經被孔劉淘汰了，好傷心」，孔劉果然是韓國現在最夯的大叔，讓人人都想競爭女朋友之位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6T143C2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6T143C2.jpg&h=7b95f631&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a47b879461c40fa81249611c9bbe5993a5da2d98","tid":114002,"uid":78698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"都是個性溫順、小鳥依人的女孩類型，同時<span style=\"color: red;\">很慢熱的屯門瓏門車位188萬元成交</span>他也不太會發生一見鍾情的情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf722a2da7edf12c0cac622a8fa19949d6b9c4a","tid":114002,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都是個性溫順、小鳥依人的女孩類型，同時<span style=\"color: red;\">很慢熱的屯門瓏門車位188萬元成交</span>他也不太會發生一見鍾情的情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22498ab7f0ca660645f0ea561627dbeea5b03fbc","tid":114002,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都是個性溫順、小鳥依人的女孩類型，同時<span style=\"color: red;\">很慢熱的屯門瓏門車位188萬元成交</span>他也不太會發生一見鍾情的情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又亂鳩咁copy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb39ce76dbeee4cf5859a6c3a7b20